data.enText: existing in or involving many countries

data.chText: 一支多国部队正赶往多事的地区。
data.enText: A multinational force is being sent to the trouble spot.
a company that operates in several different countries, especially a large and powerful company

tr: involving or operating in several nations or nationalities

value.def: A multinational company has branches or owns companies in many different countries.

example.tran: 福特公司和IBM公司等跨国公司

value.def: Multinational armies, organizations, or other groups involve people from several different countries.

example.ex: The US troops would be part of a multinational force.
example.tran: 美军将是多国部队的一个组成部分。

value.tran: (军队、组织或团体)人员来自不同国家的，国际的

value.def: Multinational countries or regions have a population that is made up of people of several different nationalities.

trans: 跨国公司；多国公司；康采恩；跨國公司；多国籍企业
